biography.text:
Josh Gabriel & Dave Dresden have been a duo for the last 16 years. In that time they have created many genre defining and genre defying hits such as “As The Rush Comes” “Tracking Treasure Down” and “Beautiful Things” to name 3.
 
 Their remix for Above & Beyond’s “No One On Earth” is considered an all time trance classic.
 
 They’ve also been noted for their DJing, performing 3 BBC Radio 1 Essential Mixes and winning IDMA Awards for Best American DJ twice. 
 
 Now back to making music after a brief hiatus, Josh & Dave partnered with their fans on Kickstarter to create their recently released Anjunabeats albums The Only Road (2017) and the recently released "Remedy" (2020)
 
Gabriel & Dresden are now touring behind Remedy. Check our profile page or remedyalbumtour.com to see if we are coming to your town.
